      "width": 1200,
      "height": 280,
      "content": "OpenOcta UI Redesign — Tech Style\n\nCanvas layout (all frames spread out, no overlap):\n  Row 0  y=0     Brief (this note)\n  Row 1  y=300   Message 1440×900 | Overview 1440×900 | Components 3060+\n  Row 2  y=1280  Tokens 680×520 | Light 680×420 | Layout note\n\nGoal: Keep shell layout unchanged. Tech/developer-tool visual language.\n\nReference: http://localhost:5173/message\n\nCanvas layout (all frames spread, no overlap):\n  Row 0  y=0     Brief (900×280)\n  Row 1  y=300   Message 1440×900 | Overview 1440×900 | Components 3060+\n  Row 2  y=1280  Tokens 680×520 | Light 680×420 | Layout note 460×200\n\nImplementation: ui/src/styles/base.css + tech-theme.css"
    },
